Enwere oke mmekọrịta n'etiti ọrịa shuga na ịwa ọkpụkpụ dịka dịbịa bekee Amaechi Nwachukwu si kwuo. Ozugbo ọrịa shuga bụrụ nke mgbanwoju anya, e kwesịrị igbupụ ukwu o metutara iji chekwaa ndụ onye ọrịa.
