Oriakụ Kehinde Gbelee, onye gbanarịrị ọrịa a afọ iri abụọ na-aga n’ihu n'ike, kwuru na mgbochi mbụ chebere ndụ ya mana ịda mba fọrọ nta ka o were ya…
