N'agbata ikpeazụ ya na mpụta LP mbụ, Blaqbonez bụụrụ onye na-adị uchu. N’ọdịnihu, ọ nwere ike ịtụle ịga n’ụzọ Olamide ma nabata ịbụ abụ.
N'ezie, ọ nọwoorị n'ọzụzụ n'ụzọ ahụ, otu n'ime ọrụ abụọ na-apụta tupu njedebe nke afọ ga-egosipụta oke ngbanwe ya, Mr Boombastic.
“Mr Boombastic bụ onye na-agba egwu. Ọ bụ onye dị mma.” Blaqbonez kwuru.
